Adcionar linhas no arquivo jdbc.properties no PDI : 

DataVault/type=javax.sql.DataSource
DataVault/driver=org.postgresql.Driver
DataVault/url=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/data_vault
DataVault/user=postgres
DataVault/password=postgres

JNDI_VERTICA/type=javax.sql.DataSource
JNDI_VERTICA/driver=com.vertica.jdbc.Driver
JNDI_VERTICA/url=jdbc:vertica://172.25.129.184:5433/dwlocal
JNDI_VERTICA/user=dbadmin
JNDI_VERTICA/password=1234
